{"tid":1536723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再講「黑警、知法犯法」呢啲垃圾說話","createTime":"2019-09-03T17:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T09:30:59.000Z","uid":156632,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"dcdc8804f431fb92609cd7bd857e4370bf6f505e","tid":1536723,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:00:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">黑警、黑社會、知法犯法呢啲字太中性一啲威力都冇。</span><br />\n<br />\n以後正名叫「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">殺人狂</span></strong></span>」，[black]等聽到嘅市民意識到佢地幾咁癲狂，喚醒一班港豬中立廢中老[/black]<br />\n<br />\n仲可以叫佢地做「畜生」、「禽獸」<br />\n<br />\n[black]我地一直太善良正義、太唔暴力，遠遠被啲殺人狂拋離。可以做嘅隨左全力支持前線，仲[/black]可以加大屌狗力度令佢地羞愧、永世抬唔起頭做狗，同埋用語言攻勢滲透全世界對抗佢地班殺人狂！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"ca9a830f75f94ca8c731adbd3d6a2eb6a3b4b325","tid":1536723,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:02:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74c8d089a03128e48aff13e8320e8377f7e66255","tid":1536723,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:03:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港警賊 子女被殺</span>"},{"pid":"52f590c55fae504ddefd15d9f90259d78e08cf5f","tid":1536723,"uid":88768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:05:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">太子殺人犯</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>1669 鍾國恩 警長<br />\n48958 李彼得 高級警員<br />\n54538 張文麟 高級警員<br />\n58248 梁智顯 高級警員 <br />\n52080 張達雄 高級警員<br />\n再加 8692 輔警 (未confirm)<br />\n<br />\n一定要推阿！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n推！！太子有片 六個殺人犯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536563\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536563</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"da787e3094b9d269988fdbabddaeff6f3a7d5844","tid":1536723,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T17:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqNCcpj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqNCcpj.jpg&h=145b357e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f583d912d86081040e06cc1cd6041d0f3e07d191","tid":1536723,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB